text: The Union Party' (; "Dashink" kusaktsutiun) is a political party in Armenia. ==History== Following the 2007 Armenian parliamentary elections the party did not win any seats in the National Assembly with a popular vote of 2.44%. The party has not participated in any elections since. ==See also== *Politics of Armenia *Programs of political parties in Armenia Category:Political parties in Armenia Category:Political parties with year of establishment missing
title: Union Party (Armenia)
